{Speech 2}{}{I beg your pardon, how may I serve you?}
{Speech 2 Answer 7}{}{Can I take a look at what you've got?}
{Speech 2 Answer 3}{}{What is this place?}
{Speech 2 Answer Exit}{}{Nothing, thanks.}
{Speech 3}{}{Refit Service A... we supply the town with tools and equipment for repairs. Are you sure you've come to the right place?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit}{}{Yes, absolutely. May I see what you have?}
{Speech 3 Answer Exit*}{}{Hardly. Goodbye.}
{Speech 7}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 7 Answer 13}{}{I see. And how are things going for you?}
{Speech 7 Answer 10}{}{In more detail?}
{Speech 7 Answer 14}{}{Tell me about the Church's farm.}
{Speech 7 Answer 8}{}{Cool story. Oh, I meant to say, I've never heard anything more boring in my life. [Exit]}
{Speech 8}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 10}{}{about the church}
{Speech 10 Answer 12}{}{Now I understand. And how are things going for you?}
{Speech 10 Answer Exit}{}{That's all I wanted to know. [Exit]}
{Speech 10 Answer 8}{}{The most boring story of my life. [Exit]}
{Speech 5}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 5 Answer 9}{}{Here, take this. A successful sermon}
{Speech 5 Answer 7}{}{Jericho, can I ask you something?}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{No, haven't found it yet. [Exit]}
{Speech 9}{}{sermon}
{Speech 6}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Everything is just wonderful. But I'm in a hurry. [Exit]}
{Speech 6 Answer 11}{}{All by God's grace. Do you need any help?}
{Speech 6 Answer 7}{}{Jericho, can I ask you something?}
{Speech 11}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 11 Answer Exit}{}{Well, that's fine. [Exit]}
{Speech 12}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 12 Answer 3}{}{Answer text}
{Speech 12 Answer 7}{}{I want to ask one more thing}
{Speech 12 Answer Exit}{}{Answer text}
{Speech 12 Answer 8}{}{Answer text}
{Speech 13}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 13 Answer 3}{}{Then why is the pen so dirty?}
{Speech 13 Answer 7}{}{I want to ask one more thing}
{Speech 13 Answer 15}{}{I bet you gather broc and xander?}
{Speech 13 Answer Exit}{}{We'll talk later. [Exit]}
{Speech 14}{}{Dialogue text}
{Speech 14 Answer 7}{}{Yes, I see you've settled in nicely... Can I ask another question?}
{Speech 14 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks, that's all I wanted to know.}
{Speech 15}{}{Sacred plants? Yes, I gather them for the monastery's needs.}
{Speech 15 Answer 16}{}{Can you share some with me?}
{Speech 16}{}{You understand, not for free. I'll let you have broc flowers for 250 coins per 25 pieces, xander roots - 125 coins per 25 pieces.}
{Speech 16 Answer 17}{}{Come on, no cheaper at all?}
{Speech 16 Answer 18}{}{All right, give me broc flowers. [Give 500 coins]}
{Speech 16 Answer 18*}{}{All right, give me xander roots. [Give 250 coins]}
{Speech 16 Answer 7}{}{All right, I'd better ask something else...}
{Speech 17}{}{All right, for you - broc at 300 coins, xander at 150}
{Speech 17 Answer 18}{}{All right, give me broc flowers. [Give 300 coins]}
{Speech 17 Answer 18*}{}{All right, give me xander roots. [Give 250 coins]}
{Speech 17 Answer 7}{}{I changed my mind.}
{Speech 18}{}{I hope you'll use them wisely.}
{Speech 18 Answer 7}{}{Let me ask one more thing.}
{Speech 18 Answer Exit}{}{Thanks, I'll be going.}
